verbose_text: Despite these methodological problems, multiple prospective studies were still able to confirm that fish consumption reduces the risk of disease progression in AMD.23, 107, 119, 123, 124, 125, 126, 127 Consumption of 1-2 servings fish per week has an OR of 0.48-0.58 for developing late AMD over 10 years of follow-up.
